These directories hold the source and interface for each Gnusto component.

NAME     USED?  PURPOSE
beret    yes    the sorting mechanism for files based on magic numbers
doer     no     experimental command interface
engine   yes    the z-code engine (will one day be engine/zcode)
errorbox yes    shows, formats and logs error messages
glulx    no     the Glulx engine (will one day be engine/glulx)
gparams  yes    parameter storage
replayer yes    plays through files
robmiz   no     experimental assembler
screen   no     screen handlers; currently done in chrome
service  yes    Moz command-line and special MIME types

